Berber Tagine


INGREDIENTS

500g Chicken/Lamb
Garlic, minced
Onion, minced
Tomato, diced
Green Beans
Zucchini
Carrot
Potatoes
Peppers
Parsley
Cilantro
Olives
1tsp Ground Ginger
1tsp Turmeric
1tsp Paprika
1tsp Cumin
1tsp Cayenne
1 Pinch Saffron
Salt & Paepper


MISE

Slice Zucchini
Slice Potatoes
Mince Garlic
Mince Onion
Slice Pepper into Rings
Slice Carrot
Dice Tomato
Chop Parsley
Show Olives
Mix
	Ground Ginger
	Turmeric
	Paprika
	Cumin
	Cayenne
	Salt & Paepper
	Olive Oil


COOK

Cast Iron Skillet
Add Onion
Add Garlic
Add Tomato
Saut√© until soft
Add 1/2 of Seasoning	
Add Chicken
Add Carrots
Add Potato
Add Zucchini
Add Pepper
Add Parsley
Pour 1/2 Seasoning Over Top
Add Olives
Cover
Cook for 45min-1hr